---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /
isHome: true
---

<section
  class="scene hero text-left page"
  data-scene
  data-kind="hero"
  data-side="right"
  data-index="00"
  data-title="Personal blog"
  data-subtitle="{{ site.alias }} · {{ site.year }} · 先想明白，再写清楚"
>
  <div class="scene-copy" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow">00 / Personal blog</span>
    <h1>先想明白，<br /><span>再写清楚。</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-note">开发、设计与思考，都只为留下下一次更好的判断。</p>
  </div>
  <span class="scroll-cue">向下，继续阅读</span>
</section>

<section
  class="scene text-right page"
  id="writing"
  data-scene
  data-kind="writing"
  data-side="left"
  data-index="01"
  data-title="Selected writing"
  data-subtitle="写下已经理解的，也保留尚未想明白的"
>
  <div class="scene-copy" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow">01 / Selected writing</span>
    <h2>最近关注的，<span>三个方向。</span></h2>
    <p class="scene-note">把已经理解的写清楚，也把尚未想明白的问题留在这里。不追求覆盖所有变化，只选择真正值得反复思考的主题，并留下能够继续延展的线索。</p>
  </div>
</section>

{% for direction in directions %}
  {% set post = collections.posts | findByCategory(direction.key) %}
  {% set i = loop.index0 %}
  {% set sceneNo = (loop.index + 1) | padNum(2) %}
  {% set textSide = "text-left" if (i % 2 == 0) else "text-right" %}
  {% set sceneSide = "right" if (i % 2 == 0) else "left" %}
  <article
    class="scene {{ textSide }} page"
    data-scene
    data-kind="{{ direction.slug }}"
    data-side="{{ sceneSide }}"
    data-index="{{ sceneNo }}"
    data-title="{{ direction.en }}"
    data-subtitle="{{ direction.subtitle }}"
  >
    <div class="scene-copy" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">{{ sceneNo }} / {{ direction.en }}</span>
      <h3>{{ direction.lead }}<span>{{ direction.muted }}</span></h3>
      {% if post %}
        <div class="article-meta">
          {{ post.templateContent | readingTime }} MIN READ · {{ post.date | readableDate }}
        </div>
        <a class="article-link" href="{{ post.url }}">阅读全文 <span>↗</span></a>
      {% else %}
        <div class="article-meta">Coming soon</div>
        <a class="article-link" href="/{{ direction.slug }}/" aria-label="查看{{ direction.key }}列表">查看列表 <span>↗</span></a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </article>
{% endfor %}

{% set aboutNo = (directions.length + 2) | padNum(2) %}
<section
  class="scene about-scene text-right page"
  id="about"
  data-scene
  data-kind="about"
  data-side="left"
  data-index="{{ aboutNo }}"
  data-title="About"
  data-subtitle="关于{{ site.name }}，以及这个博客为什么存在"
>
  <div class="scene-copy" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow">{{ aboutNo }} / About</span>
    <h2 class="about-title">
      <span class="name-line">{{ site.name }}</span>
      <span class="alias-line">{{ site.alias }}</span>
      <span class="focus-line">开发 · 设计 · 思考</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="about-bottom">
      <p>这里收录我对系统、智能与界面的长期观察。不追求覆盖所有变化，只记录那些值得被反复思考、不断修正，并最终写清楚的问题。</p>
      <a class="contact" href="{{ site.github }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub ↗</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
